        &lt;h4&gt;Order imbalance for each quote at the best limits. The blue (red) dots represent Buy (Sell) market orders. The dots size are proportional the trade volumes.&lt;/h4&gt;
        
    &lt;/figcaption&gt;
    
&lt;/figure&gt;


